Title: Establishes the Wheatland-Scottsville Joint Fire District
Summary: Establishes the Wheatland-Scottsville Joint Fire District; provides for the dissolution of the town of Wheatland fire protection district located in the town of Wheatland, Monroe county, New York, and the establishment of the Wheatland-Scottsville joint fire district by the town board of the Town of Wheatland, and the board of trustees of the village of Scottsville, Monroe county.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to the establishment of the Wheatland-Scottsville joint fire district
